{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_15", "eventName": "解離重組", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "15-8", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "破碎迴響", "storyInfo": "博士與阿米婭在黑王冠儲存的資訊中見到了普瑞賽斯的身影，也從預言家的實驗記錄片段中得到了需要的知識。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "avg_ac8mi_Pre", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這幅畫面明明就在你們的眼前，但卻又無論如何也無法接近。"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，和那個人交談的人……是你？", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "……;無法確定。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line13", "option2": "line13"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）我並不認為僅靠我自己就能創造出一門足以闡述終極答案的語言。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）至少，同胞們共享的各領域最頂尖研究成果已經為我搭建了繼續深入的平台。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）哪怕最後還是一無所獲？", "name": "預言家"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）嗯，反正又不是第一次了。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）在安靜等待黑暗吞噬我們的這段日子裡，我們似乎也沒有更好的辦法了不是嗎？", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）況且，我確定你不會拒絕我，{@nickname}。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "預言家"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）你準備從什麼地方開始研究？", "name": "預言家"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "普瑞賽斯沒有回答，只是看著天邊隱隱的朝霞。而她身旁的那個人也並未打擾她。"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩人只是那樣站在甲板上。"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看著她的背影，下意識地告訴自己：“她又在思考了”——"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "……", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line27"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼你會突然這樣想？"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，你怎麼了？", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "沒什麼，只是走神。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line32"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 33, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "我想這裡沒有更重要的線索了。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line35"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱爾希醫生在意的資訊並不在這裡？", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "這應當是源石誕生之前的歷史碎片。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line39"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……？！", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "是結合我在內化宇宙中的經歷作出的推測。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line43"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的意思是，我們現在所捕獲到的這個畫面資訊是因為博士你……", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "恐怕不只這個。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line47"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——那艘飄浮在空中的巨大艦船和碎裂的壯觀球體難道也……", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "我並不清楚自己和這些資訊的關聯是什麼。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line51"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們總會弄清楚的，博士。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但既然你已經確認這裡不是我們的重點，那就繼續前進吧。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "60_i04", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.0, "yScaleFrom": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 1.2, "yScaleTo": 1.2, "duration": 100.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"xstrength": 3.0, "ystrength": 2.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 60.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$shatterpoint_02_intro", "key": "$shatterpoint_02_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奇點近在眼前，但構建的通路也瀕臨極限。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡的資訊密度實在太高，繼續前進的感覺就好像是溺在一條很深的河流裡。", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我們要如何從這些混亂資訊中分辨出我們所需要的？", "name": "阿米婭"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "交給我吧。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line70"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們的思維正無限逼近奇點，近乎實體的巨量資訊擠壓著你們……"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "儘管你似乎能夠完全適應這種壓力，但你也察覺到阿米婭正在苦苦支撐。"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "留給你們的時間並不多。"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.0, "xstrength": 3.0, "ystrength": 2.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 60.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "60_i05", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_confusion_centra", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_confusion_loop", "layer": 3.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你抽取了內化宇宙中那位“普瑞賽斯”所說的每一個關鍵字，並快速將凱爾希留下的每一條線索聯繫起來。"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快速地演算出一個新的結果，輸入新的條件……以此循環，繼續前進，直到分離出唯一需要的資訊。"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的思維就像陷入了無邊無際的積木海洋中，而你要做的事情自始至終都並不複雜。"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "找到那個顏色不同的異類，上面工整地鐫刻著凱爾希為你留下的話語——"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "text": "“我從未忘記。”", "x": 320.0, "y": 340.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.001, "width": 700.0, "block": "true", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "duration": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "阿米婭，我想我們成功了。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line95"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 96, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "60_g1_rhodescorridor_bc", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$calm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#5$2", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這裡是，什麼地方？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#5$2"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "羅德島。;過去的羅德島。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line113", "option2": "line113"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#5$2"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——？！", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#5$2"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#10$2"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但這和我們的羅德島——", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#10$2"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "天差地別。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line121"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#7$2"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱爾希醫生提起過，本艦最初是從雷姆必拓挖掘出來並加以修繕才投入了使用。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#7$2"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那……羅德島到底經歷了什麼？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#7$2"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "我也毫無頭緒。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line128"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）你今天的精神看起來很不錯，看來我們的努力很成功。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）是獨自待在實驗室會害怕嗎？", "name": "預言家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（驕傲的嗡鳴）", "name": "原始構造體"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）剛好，我正在推演這個用於減少元資料在特殊媒介中損耗的模型，可以試著幫我運算嗎？", "name": "預言家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（焦躁地抖動）", "name": "原始構造體"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）足夠了，我已強制終止你的程式。", "name": "預言家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）不要在任何時候傷害自己的核心元件，哪怕命令來自我或是她。", "name": "預言家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）保護你自己，AMa-10，生存才是生命誕生時便擁有的本能。", "name": "預言家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（不甘的嗡鳴）", "name": "原始構造體"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知語言）哈哈，至少情感模組的自我迭代速度很快。", "name": "預言家"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#7$2"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，你能理解這種語言嗎？", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#7$2"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "不能。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line156"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 157, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "不必關注那個人和旁邊的奇怪造物。;關鍵在其他地方。", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line160", "option2": "line160"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "的確，凱爾希醫生既然相信我們能夠找到關鍵，語言的阻礙應該已經在她的預計之中。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，注意看那個人旁邊的玻璃，上面寫滿了很多文字。", "name": "阿米婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_1037_amiya3_1#1$2"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "公式？", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line167"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1360_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（未知